# Spawning and Populating

Spawn an Actor and add it to the System's view

    spawn SomeActor populateView

Spawn an Actor, add it to the System's view, and assign it an Address

    spawn
        SomeActor
        (\pid ->
            batch
                [ populateView pid
                , populateAddress pid
                ]
        )

